profile:
Specializing in the refinishing of counter tops, back splashes, tiles... using earth friendly products from EcoRefinishers. I use a paint process in which I go over the old arborite and tile that leaves the old surface looking like granite. Over 60 colors to choose from.  The surface is cured and ready to use upon completion, 1-2 days depending on the size. Reface Don't Replace.
 $20 per sq ft
name: D.Williams Refinishing
